<title>AUSTRALIA: RTRS-Ashton extends ADE bid by one week.</title>
<headline>RTRS-Ashton extends ADE bid by one week.</headline>
<dateline>MELBOURNE 1997-02-20</dateline>
<text>
<p>Ashton Mining Ltd said on Thursday its takeover bid for its Australian Diamond Exploration NL subsidiary will now close one week later on March 3.</p>
<p>Ashton has offered A$1.40 per share for ADE, which ended nine cents higher atA$1.40.</p>
<p>ADE's independent directors have recommended the bid by Ashton, which launched the offer in November already owning a 77.6 percent stake and which is now entitled to 87.3 percent.</p>
<p>-- Sydney Newsroom 61-2 9373-1800</p>
